Uses of Package
entities

Packages that use entities
Package Description
controller
Contains game phases, game engine and user command to start the game and to execute the commands.
entities
Contains basic entities used in the game like countries, continents, map and player.
entities.mapops
Contains map operations related to map.
entities.orders
Contains all the orders which the user provides during game phase.
entities.savedgames
Contains the classes used to Save the game for future aspects and Load the game to resume playing.
strategy  
  • Classes in entities used by controller
    Class Description
    GameMap
    GameMap which holds variables which contains information continents, countries and neighbourhood between countries.
    Player
    Player in a game contains information about the continents and countries controlled by player, cards the player have, method to order input from user, queue to store player order and number of reinforcement armies player have.
